formula: Branch B (+1,-1): Piecewise closed-form solution with switch logic. V(t) = V(0)=3.890413 for t<0; V(t) = T(σ^prev)/(1-β) + [V_B(t*) - T(σ^prev)/(1-β)]exp(λ(σ^prev)(t-t*)) for 0≤t≤t*; V(t) = c₀/(1-β) + (a_B c₁)/(1-β)²[1-exp(λ_B(t-1))] + (c₁/(1-β))t for t*≤t≤1; V(t) = V(1)=3.250000 for t>1.
